===================

Askisi 4:

Στον επόμενο πίνακα δίνονται τα ποσά των ακάλυπτων επιταγών (σε εκατ. Ευρώ) ανά εποχή από το 2017 μέχρι το 2019 Να γίνει εξάλειψη της εποχικότητας των τιμών και να προσαρμοστεί η γραμμή τάσης. Στη συνέχεια να γίνει πρόβλεψη του ποσού των ακάλυπτων επιταγών για το φθινόπωρο του 2020

Bima 1:

Fortonoume ta dedomena se ena R array.

# declare data per year
data2017 = c(190.8, 132.1, 203.9, 211.3)
data2018 = c(302.3, 203.9, 236.2, 271.4)
data2019 = c(320.9, 250, 248.9, 280.3)

# combin data
data = append(data2017, data2018)
data = append(data, data2019)

data
 [1] 190.8 132.1 203.9 211.3 302.3 203.9 236.2 271.4 320.9 250.0 248.9 280.3

Bima 2:

Pragmatopoioume elenxo ton dedomenon gia tin kaliteri katanoisi tous: - Elenxoume an ta data einai xronoseira. - Provaloume tin xronoseira - Ipologizoume ta ACF kai PACF

x=ts(data)

# plot cmort data
plot.ts(x, main="Dataset")


# plot PACF 
acf2(x)
     [,1] [,2]  [,3] [,4]  [,5]  [,6]
ACF  0.33 0.12 -0.04 0.20 -0.04 -0.24
PACF 0.33 0.01 -0.09 0.26 -0.21 -0.25

Bima 3:

Paratiroume oti i xronosira den einai stasimi. Diladi:

  • Parateoume oti sta dedomena ipaexei epoxikotita kai poio sigkekrimena quarterly seasonality diladi S = 4.
  • Episis Paratirite kai mia anodiki tasi stin xronosira

Arxika provaloume tin euthia tis tasis kanontas decompose ta data mas

ts_data = ts(data, freq = 4)
decomp_data = decompose (ts_data, type = "multiplicative")
plot (decomp_data)

plot (decomp_data$trend)

Epilisi tou parapano thematos Gia na epilisoume to parapano thema litourgoume ws eksis: 1. Dilonoume oti i xronosira exei sixnotita 4 (dedomenou oti exei quardatic trend) 2. Apalifoume tin epoxikotita pernontas tis 4es diafores 3. Apalifoume tin tasi pernontas tin 1i diafora afou exoume parei tis 4 diafores

# take 4th diffs to remove seasonality from data
diff4 = diff(x, 4)
plot.ts(diff4)

# take 1st diffs to remove trend from data
diff1and4 = diff(diff4,1)
plot.ts(diff1and4)


acf2(diff1and4)
      [,1] [,2]  [,3]  [,4]  [,5]
ACF  -0.61 0.39 -0.24 -0.02  0.03
PACF -0.61 0.02  0.01 -0.28 -0.14

Fit Arima model

Apo ta PCF kai PACF simperenoume oti ena pithano montelo tha mporouse na einai to AR(2)

# apply diff data on ARIMA(2,0,0)
fitARIMA <- arima(diff1and4, order=c(2,0,2), seasonal = c(1,0,0))
